      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Irene Lucas is a non-executive board member of the Department for Education. She joined in November 2018.</p>

<p>Irene has a range of experience. She is the chair of the Hays Travel group, a board member of Sport England and The Academy for Sustainable Communities and was a director general at the Department of Communities and Local Government.</p>

<p>Irene received a CBE for services to local government in 2008.</p>
</div>
      </section>

